<h3 id='is_sliding'>: is_sliding()</h3><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight lua tab-lua"><code><span class="kd">local</span>   <span class="p">;</span><span class="c1">-- example </span>
<span class="kd">local</span> <span class="n">is__sliding</span> <span class="o">=</span>     <span class="p">;:</span><span class="n">is_sliding</span><span class="p">()</span>
</code></pre></div>
<p>Queries whether or not this  is currently <em>sliding</em>.<br>
Returns <code>true</code> if they are, otherwise <code>false</code>.</p>
<h4 id='function-call'>Function Call</h4>
<p><code>:is_sliding()</code></p>
<h4 id='return-value'>Return Value</h4>
<p><strong><code>boolean</code></strong></p>
